<P><B>Playing time:</B> 40' 14"
</P>

<P><B>Performers:</B><br>
Angelo Branduardi (voice, violin) &amp; Chominciamento di Gioia
[Elisabetta Di Filippo (psalterion, bells, percussions), Olga Ercoli
(harp), Luigi Polsini (vielle, rebec, lute, viola da gamba),
Gianfranco Russo (vielle, lyra, hurdy-gurdy, recorders, crumhorn),
Marco Salerno (cornett, lute, saz), Cristina Scrima (recorders,
transverse flute, bombard, crumhorn), Pier Carlo Zanco (violone,
percussions)] - Renato Serio, dir.
</P>

